837
00:37:51,752 --> 00:37:53,987
I was really shy,

838
00:37:53,988 --> 00:37:56,590
And it made people
think I was weird,

839
00:37:56,591 --> 00:37:58,525
So they left me alone.

840
00:37:58,526 --> 00:38:02,562
And it wasn't until I joined
glee club that I realized

841
00:38:02,563 --> 00:38:06,099
How much I was missing.

842
00:38:06,100 --> 00:38:07,634
And I don't want to push
people away anymore.

843
00:38:09,170 --> 00:38:11,238
You understand what
that's like, don't you?

844
00:38:11,239 --> 00:38:14,007
No, I don't.

845
00:38:15,409 --> 00:38:17,244
I would never try
to push people away

846
00:38:17,245 --> 00:38:19,346
'cause being in a chair
kind of does that for you.

